  "detailHtml": "<p><img src=\"/assets/images/m-files/530288607-afc8695d1e794748af05abd82b0ddf3e_cca4198d.png\" alt=\"\"></p><h2 data-path-to-node=\"9\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kits AI 高级会员 (30天保固)</span></h2><h3 data-path-to-node=\"10\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">核心权益</span></h3><ul data-path-to-node=\"11\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">三档创作规格可选：提供 <strong data-path-to-node=\"11,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"12\">Starter (基础版), Producer (制作人版), 或 Professional (专业版)</strong> 三档 30 天会员规格，请根据您的音频产出与克隆需求按需购买。</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">顶尖 AI 声音克隆与歌声合成：全面解锁全自动即时声音克隆（Starter规格）与工作室级专业声音克隆（Producer/Professional规格）；专享高阶 AI 歌声合成器（Singing Voice Synthesizer）与高阶合唱编排工具（Choir Tool），为音乐创作者提供无限高质量人声素材。</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">无限制音频转换与超大下载：全系享有无限制的音频对音频（Audio-to-Audio）声音转换频次。基础版专享 2 个声音训练槽位与 15 分钟音频下载，制作人版尊享无限槽位与 60 分钟下载，专业版尊享无限槽位与无限制音频下载时长。</span></p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"12\" style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">发货须知</span></h3><ul data-path-to-node=\"13\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"margin-top: 5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">官方网址：</span><response-element class=\"\" ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\"><link-block _nghost-ng-c399922553=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><a _ngcontent-ng-c399922553=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" externallink=\"\" _nghost-ng-c3958779587=\"\" jslog=\"197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_78f92a91803209bf&quot;,&quot;c_60a5a2a67956c741&quot;,null,&quot;rc_736fc9182326ee3b&quot;,null,null,&quot;zh-Hani&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]\" href=\"https://www.kits.ai/\" clas